r: #9876AA">apache_get_modules</span><span style="color: #007700">());<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span> </span> </code></div>     </div>      <div class="example-contents"><p>以上例程的输出类似于：</p></div>     <div class="example-contents screen"> <div class="cdata"><pre> Array (     [0] =&gt; core     [1] =&gt; http_core     [2] =&gt; mod_so     [3] =&gt; sapi_apache2     [4] =&gt; mod_mime     [5] =&gt; mod_rewrite ) </pre></div>     </div>    </div>   </p>  </div>  <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.apache.php">Apache 函数</a></div></div>
